Ingredients 50 ml Inverroche Gin Classic 150 ml Tonic water 10 ml Cointreau Orange Liqueur 10 ml Kahlua Coffee liqueur 30 ml Cold coffee/espresso ( pour over ice to chill and strain, or use Cold Brewed coffee) Method Select a generous whisky tumbler and add lots of very cold ice. Pour the gin over the ice and add the tonic water. In a second mixing glass, combine and stir the Cointreau and Kahlua with ice in the mixing glass until chilled. Strain the mixture carefully into the G&T and garnish with a brul√©ed orange slice, a long curl or a twist of orange zest and a cinnamon stick.